snippet.title: Scorcher Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Scorcher is an all-new blazing-fast infinite canyon racer from Radiangames.

Coming to iOS March 7th, 2019!  Jump into your Scorcher and blast through canyons at insane speeds.  Take out rogue sandsharks while avoiding colossal sandworms and survive as long as you can!

Get it here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/scorcher/id1451321578
